Source: webcleaner
Section: web
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Bastian Kleineidam <calvin@debian.org>
Standards-Version: 3.5.5
Build-Depends: python2-base, debhelper (>= 3.0.0), debconf

Package: webcleaner
Architecture: any
Depends: python2-base, python2-zlib, debconf
Suggests: webcleanerconf
Description: a filtering HTTP proxy
 Features:
  o disable animated GIFs
  o on-the-fly compression of documents
  o privacy (remove user-agent: header and obfuscate IP address)
  o can remove all HTML crap (adverts, javascript, ...)
  o completely customizable

Package: webcleanerconf
Architecture: all
Depends: python2-base, python-fox (>= 0.99.172), webcleaner
Description: configuration tool for webcleaner
 This is a nice GUI configuration tool for the WebCleaner proxy.
